PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774699372
OL,3,CIsrael stops missile fired from Yemen
OL,4,Cas Houthi rebels claim responsibility
OL,6,FThe Houthis, a rebel group backed by
OL,7,FTehran who have held Yemen's capital
OL,8,Fsince 2014, have claimed
OL,9,Fresponsibility for the attack.
OL,11,FBrig. Gen. Yahya Saree, a military
OL,12,Fspokesman for the Houthis, issued the
OL,13,Fclaim in a statement aired Saturday
OL,14,Fmorning by the rebels' Al-Masirah
OL,15,Fsatellite television.
OL,17,FIt comes as Iran claimed some of its
OL,18,Fnuclear facilities were hit by
OL,19,Fstrikes, as well as two of the
OL,20,Fnation's largest steel factories.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774699372
OL,3,CIsrael stops missile fired from Yemen
OL,4,Cas Houthi rebels claim responsibility
OL,6,FIran's Atomic Energy Organization said
OL,7,Fthe strikes didn't cause any
OL,8,Fcasualties or risk of contamination.
OL,10,FAlso on Friday, an Iranian missile
OL,11,Fattack left at least 15 US service
OL,12,Fmembers wounded, including five
OL,13,Fseriously.
OL,15,FIran fired six ballistic missiles and
OL,16,F29 drones at Saudi Arabia's Prince
OL,17,FSultan air base and damaged several
OL,18,Fplanes at a military base in Saudi
OL,19,FArabia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
