PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774699372
OL,3,CIsrael stops missile fired from Yemen
OL,4,Cas Houthi rebels claim responsibility
OL,6,FUS officials initially reported that
OL,7,Fat least 10 US troops were injured,
OL,8,Fincluding two seriously wounded.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, US Secretary of State Marco
OL,11,FRubio has said the conflict in the
OL,12,FMiddle East will end in "weeks not
OL,13,Fmonths" after a meeting with his G7
OL,14,Fcounterparts on Friday.
OL,16,FSpeaking to reporters after the
OL,17,Fearlier G7 meeting in France
OL,18,Fconcluded, Rubio said: "We are very
OL,19,Fconfident we are on the verge of
OL,20,Fachieving them (aims) very soon."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774699372
OL,3,CIsrael stops missile fired from Yemen
OL,4,Cas Houthi rebels claim responsibility
OL,6,FWhen asked how long until the conflict
OL,7,Fended, Rubio said: "We are talking
OL,8,Fweeks, not months."
OL,10,FHe also said the US can achieve its
OL,11,Fmilitary aims "without any ground
OL,12,Ftroops", amid speculation the US was
OL,13,Fconsidering putting boots on the
OL,14,Fground in Iran, with thousands of
OL,15,FAmerican marines moved to the area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
