PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774699372
OL,3,CIsrael stops missile fired from Yemen
OL,4,Cas Houthi rebels claim responsibility
OL,6,FOn Thursday, US President Donald Trump
OL,7,Fagain extended his self-imposed
OL,8,Fdeadline for Tehran to reopen the
OL,9,FStrait of Hormuz.
OL,11,FTrump said talks to end the war are
OL,12,F"going very well," but Iran continues
OL,13,Fto publicly insist it is not
OL,14,Fnegotiating with the White House.
OL,16,FHe complained that Nato and European
OL,17,Fnations have ignored or rejected
OL,18,Frequests for help confronting Tehran's
OL,19,Fretaliation, including the closure of
OL,20,Fthe Strait of Hormuz to most
OL,21,Finternational shipping.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
