OL,3,CIsrael stops missile fired from Yemen
OL,4,Cas Houthi rebels claim responsibility
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FTrump said: "We are very disappointed
OL,12,Fwith Nato because Nato has done
OL,13,Fabsolutely nothing."
OL,15,FHe also criticised the UK's response
OL,16,Fto the conflict and compared the UK's
OL,17,Faircraft carriers to "toys."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
