OL,3,CIsrael stops missile fired from Yemen
OL,4,Cas Houthi rebels claim responsibility
OL,6,FSince the war began, more than 1,900
OL,7,Fpeople have been killed in Iran,
OL,8,Faccording to the Health Ministry,
OL,9,Fwhile 1,100 people have died in
OL,10,FLebanon, 18 in Israel and at least 13
OL,11,Fservice members from the US.
OL,13,FThe International Organization for
OL,14,FMigration said Friday that 82,000
OL,15,Fcivilian buildings, including
OL,16,Fhospitals and the homes of 180,000
OL,17,Fpeople, have been damaged in Iran so
OL,18,Ffar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
